AI-based tools were used selectively during the preparation of this thesis in an assistive role. They supported language refinement, structural review, consistency checks, the organization of notes and feedback material, and the preparation of review prompts and checklists during the writing process.

All AI-generated suggestions were reviewed, selected, and revised by the authors. The authors remain responsible for the final wording, the technical descriptions, the interpretation of feedback, and the correct use of sources. AI tools were not used as independent sources of factual claims; factual statements are based on cited literature, project documentation, implementation work, and feedback material.
